TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: M hnh ho in ton sng m - m my v bi ton lp lch tc v nhiu
rng buc.
Tc gi lun vn: on Ho Khim. Kho: 2019A.
Ngi hng dn: PGS.TS. Nguyn Bnh Minh.
T kha (Keyword): in ton m my, in ton sng m m my, bi ton lp
lch, gii thut metaheuristic.
Ni dung tm tt:
a) L do chn ti
in ton sng m (fog computing) ln u tin c Cisco nh ngha vo nm
2015. n nay, in ton sng m tr thnh t kho y ha hn c cng ng
tm kim v gii hc thut dnh nhiu thi gian nghin cu, th nghim. Tuy nhin
cng ngh ny vn cha thc s tr thnh mt tiu chun p dng vo vn hnh sn
xut. Chnh v vy y vn cn l ti m cho cc c nhn, t chc tham gia nghin
cu m hnh ny ngy mt hon thin hn. Lun vn mong mun ng gp mt
phn sc lc vo s nghip nghin cu v pht trin khoa hc, k thut ca Vit Nam
ni ring cng nh ton th gii ni chung.
b) Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu.
Mc ch chnh l tm hiu cng ngh in ton m my, in ton sng m
m my. Cc kt qu cn t c:
o Hiu r hot ng ca cc h thng ny.
o xut m hnh cho h thng v bi ton lp lch nhiu rng buc.
o Th nghim v so snh cc gii thut trn m hnh xut.
i tng nghin cu l cc h thng in ton c cng nh mi c nghin
cu gn y.
Phm vi nghin cu tp trung chnh vo xut m hnh v bi ton lp lch. Bn
cnh l mt s gii thut metaheuristic cng vi cc th nghim, nh gi.
c) Tm tt c ng cc ni dung chnh v ng gp mi ca tc gi
- M hnh ho mi trng nhiu rng buc ca cc h thng in ton sng m -
m my gm in nng tiu th, tr dch v v chi ph.
2
- xut s dng cc gii thut metaheuristic gii bi ton lp lch trong m hnh
sng m - m my xut.
- Gi lp h thng sng m - m my nh xut nh gi cc chin lc
lp lch tc v trn .
- Th nghim vi mt s gii thut metaheuristic cho bi ton lp lch trong mi
trng nhiu rng buc ca h thng sng m - m my.
d) Phng php nghin cu.
Nghin cu t l thuyt, cc h thng hot ng thc t n xut m hnh
n th nghim cc gii thut trn m hnh xut.
e) Kt lun
Trong lun vn ny, ti tm hiu v h thng in ton m my, cc m hnh
dch v, m hnh trin khai ca n. Cng vi l s m rng ca n ti bin ca
mng l m hnh in ton sng m m my.
Cc kt qu th nghim chng minh m hnh xut l hp l v c kh nng
ti u thng qua cc gii thut metaheuristic.
in ton sng m m my vn cn l mi v rt cn cc c nhn, t chc
dnh thi gian tm hiu, nghin cu, th nghim ngy mt hon thin. Ti rt hi
vng cng ngh ny s tr nn ph bin v phc v cuc sng hng ngy trong mt
thi gian khng xa.
